children.content: To get the most out of the Bazaarvoice platform, we must provide data about product catalog to Bazaarvoice. This includes data about - the brands - product categories - products

DATA: BRAND - Brand.externald (R) - Brand.name (R) CATEGORY (product category) - Category.externalId (R) - Category.name (R) PRODUCT - Product.externalId (R) - Product.name (R) - Product.brand (R) - Product.category (R) - Product.ImageURL (R) - Product.EAN (R*) (either UPC, or EAN or ISBN is required) - Product.UPC (R*) - Product.ISBN (R*) - Variantes
Pas de gestion "complète" de la pression de communication (litiges, ereputation...)
Pas encore prévu de rappatrier les consents sur avis produits dans la DC
